import React from 'react'
import { View ,Text, Image,TouchableOpacity} from 'react-native'

const img = require('../../assets/foodies.png')
const WelcomePage=()=> {
  return (
    <View>
        <View>
        <Text>Welcome To Foddies</Text>
        </View>
        
        <View style={{alignItems:'center',marginTop:100}}>
        <Image source={img} style={{height:100,width:'40%'}}></Image>
        <TouchableOpacity>
            <Text style={{fontWeight:800,fontSize:30}}>BreakFast</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        </View>
        <View style={{alignItems:'center'}}>
        <Image source={img} style={{height:100,width:'40%'}}></Image>
        <TouchableOpacity>
            <Text>BreakFast</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        </View>
        
    </View>
  )
}

export default WelcomePage
